---
sitemap_priority: 1.0
hide_home: hidden
wrapper_class: home
layout: layout
---

-# @spec HOME-UI-003 HOME-UI-004 HOME-UI-005 HOME-UI-006
.profile-strip
  %img.avatar{src: url_for('/images/dwf.png'), srcset: "#{url_for '/images/dwf@2x.png'} 2x", alt: "Davis's Profile Photo"}
  .profile-text
    %h1 Hello, I'm Davis.
    %p
      You may know me from my time at Pivotal Labs, where I helped build Rails and mobile apps,
      or from co-writing Jasmine, a JavaScript testing framework.
      This is where I write about software engineering, leadership, and occasional digressions.

-# @spec HOME-UI-007 HOME-UI-008 HOME-UI-009 HOME-UI-010 HOME-UI-011 HOME-UI-012 RFCT-UI-001 RFCT-UI-002
.home-grid
  .recent-posts
    %h2 Recent Posts
    -# @spec RFCT-UI-006
    - blog.articles.first(3).each do |article|
      .post-entry
        %h3
          %a.title{href: article.url}= article.title
        - if article.data.teaser
          %p.teaser= teaser_for(article.data)
        %p.date
          = article.date.strftime('%-d %B %Y')
          %span.sep ·
          = reading_time_for article.body
    .more
      %a{href: "/posts"} All Posts →

  .series-list
    %h2 Series
    - data.series.each do |slug, series|
      .series-entry
        %h3
          %a.series-title{href: "/series/#{slug}"}= series.title
        %p.series-teaser= series.teaser
    .more
      %a{href: "/series"} All Series →
